name: C L A R I T Y / /
description: A shining body of crystal water,  Cool to the touch, perfectly unbothered,   A glimpse into the pond offers nothing at first, You lean in further with all doubts dispersed,  Memories and thoughts, rampant and shrouded, Your soundness and mind are equally clouded,  Softly glowing as you weep in sincerity, Let this tranquil beauty bring you clarity. . .   Can you see now what awaits beyond?
